---
title: Portfolio
layout: "/layouts/base.njk"
nav: true
menutitle: Home
order: 1
---


<div class="homepage-grid">
    <div class="homepage-grid__introduction">
        <h2 class="introduction--first">geffrey is a digital product designer and amateur musicologist</h2>
        <h2 class="introduction--second">a selection of digital products I helped realise</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="homepage-grid__notes">
        <h2>thoughts on music \ design \ life</h2>
        {% if collections.notes.length > 0 %}
        <div class="notes__columns">
            <ul>
            {% for note in collections.notes %}
                <li class="homepage-notes__item">
                    <a class="homepage-notes__content" href="{{ note.url }}">
                        <span class="homepage-notes__heading">{{ note.data.title }}</span>
                    </a>
                </li>
            {% endfor %}
            {% else %}
                <li style="text-align: center; margin: 0 2rem;">
                    <strong>Here's where I'd put my notes. If I had any 😤.</strong>
                </li>
            </ul>
        {% endif %}
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="homepage-grid__projects">
        {% for project in collections.projects %}
            {% set url = project.url %}
            {% set title = project.data.title %}
            {% set projectcover = project.data.projectcover %}
            {% include "components/_projectlistitem.njk" %}
        {% endfor %}
    </div>
</div>

